########################## TO SSH TO HOST ###################################
1) go to .ssh -> cd .ssh
2) command to generate ssh key -> ssh-keygen
3) just enter 3 time ssh key file is created
4) cat id_rsa.pub
5) copu the code and paste in the host file that is cd .ssh  in authorized_keys 

Ansible playbook
playbook in written in yaml or yml
location - /opt/playbooks/

